pred =  predict(glm1, TS, type="response") #預測
cm = table(actual = TS$buy, predict = pred > 0.5); cm #用TS$buy與模型預測出來的答案做混淆矩陣，thershold=0.5。
##        predict
## actual  FALSE TRUE
##   FALSE  3761  841
##   TRUE   1706 2267
acc.ts = cm %>% {sum(diag(.))/sum(.)} #準確率
c(1-mean(TS$buy) , acc.ts)  # 0.69998 準確率
## [1] 0.5366764 0.7029738
colAUC(pred, TS$buy)        # 0.7556 ROC曲線下面的面積＝AUC 在各種thershold下，可以用這個模型來解釋75%的資料

Regression Model

A2 = subset(A, A$buy) %>% mutate_at(c("m","rev","amount"), log10) #A2=購買過的資料
TR2 = subset(A2, spl2)
TS2 = subset(A2, !spl2)
lm1 = lm(amount ~ ., TR2[,c(2:6,8:10)]) # 用TR2[,c(2:6,8:10)]的欄位裡變數來預測購買金額（amount）

r2.tr = summary(lm1)$r.sq #模型可以解釋多少變異
SST = sum((TS2$amount - mean(TR2$amount))^ 2) #(每個實際值-平均amount)^2
SSE = sum((predict(lm1, TS2) -  TS2$amount)^2) #(每個實際值-每個預測值)^2
r2.ts = 1 - (SSE/SST) 
c(R2train=r2.tr, R2test=r2.ts)
##   R2train    R2test 
## 0.2783147 0.2880725

製作變數、改進模型

Fig-2: Prediction

進行預測

Aggregate data 2000-12-01 ~ 2001~02-28.

load("data/tf0.rdata")
d0 = max(X0$date) + 1
B = X0 %>% 
  filter(date >= as.Date("2000-12-01")) %>% #三個月
  mutate(days = as.integer(difftime(d0, date, units="days"))) %>% 
  group_by(cust) %>% summarise(
    r = min(days),      # recency
    s = max(days),      # seniority
    f = n(),            # frquency
    m = mean(total),    # monetary
    rev = sum(total),   # total revenue contribution
    raw = sum(gross),   # total gross profit contribution
    age = age[1],       # age group
    area = area[1],     # area code
  ) %>% data.frame      # 28584
nrow(B)
## [1] 28547

In B, there is a record for each customer. B$Buy is the probability of buying in March.

B$Buy = predict(glm1, B, type="response")  # 拿2000-12-01 ~ 2001~02-28資料加進來，預測三月可能購買的機率

💡： 預測購買金額時要記得做指數、對數轉換！

B2 = B %>% mutate_at(c("m","rev"), log10) #將c("m","rev")取log存成B
B$Rev = 10^predict(lm1, B2) #預測購買的金額
par(mfrow=c(1,2), cex=0.8)
hist(B$Buy) #會購買的機率分佈
hist(log(B$Rev,10)) #預測購買金額的分佈

save(B, file='data/tf4.rdata') #儲存檔案
